The story ends with the man committing suicide since he does not want to be with anyone else and feels hopeless. The woman goes on to make a big family with the man and lives well even after all of the trauma she experienced. It was a sad story of basically a stalker that was more persistent than most who had mental health issues. The story was very sad and the ending was not what I expected. It made me pretty sad overall and I wanted to cry.
